{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI","doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/UIKit","doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/UIKit\/UIView"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/UIKit\/UIView\/environment","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"environment"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"ViewEnvironment","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to provide overrides for the environment as it flows through a node, you should conform to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"type":"text","text":" and provide those overrides in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customize(environment:)"},{"type":"text","text":". E.g.:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["func customize(environment: inout ViewEnvironment) {","    environment.traits.mode = .dark","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, this property gets the environment by recursively walking to the root of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation path, and applying customizations on the way back down. The invalidation path may be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interrupted if a node has set it’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentAncestor"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", even if there is a node"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which specifies this node as an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentDescendant"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to update the return value of this variable and have those changes propagated through the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation hierarchy, conform to "},{"code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and call "},{"code":"setNeedsEnvironmentUpdate()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and wait"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for the system to call "},{"code":"apply(context:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" when appropriate (e.g. on the next layout pass for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"type":"text","text":"\/"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"type":"text","text":" subclasses)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"code":"UIViewController","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" conformers ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"must"}]},{"text":" call ","type":"text"},{"code":"applyEnvironmentIfNeeded()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"viewWillLayoutSubviews()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"layoutSubviews()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" respectively.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"important","name":"Important","type":"aside"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"code":"ViewEnvironment","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" that is flowing through the propagation hierarchy."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/viewenvironmentui\/uikit\/ui